Great news — on **.NET 10 SDK**, `dotnet test` has **native MTP support**, so you **no longer need `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`**.

### What to do

Add a `test` section to your **`global.json`**:

```json
{
  "sdk": {
    "version": "10.0.100"
  },
  "test": {
    "runner": "Microsoft.Testing.Platform"
  }
}
```

